WEBVTT

00:00:07.280 --> 00:00:08.079
Ling Han

00:00:09.840 --> 00:00:11.079
Why did you kill Zhou Shuyu?

00:00:14.560 --> 00:00:16.360
The shoulder line of this outfit of yours

00:00:18.040 --> 00:00:18.920
is a little crooked.

00:00:20.680 --> 00:00:22.120
It came off an assembly line, right?

00:00:24.559 --> 00:00:25.680
Good clothes

00:00:26.680 --> 00:00:27.680
have life.

00:00:34.400 --> 00:00:35.240
Answer the question.

00:00:36.599 --> 00:00:38.279
Why did you attack Zhou Shuyu?

00:00:38.759 --> 00:00:39.680
Xiaoyu...

00:00:40.240 --> 00:00:41.919
She was my best client.

00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:44.319
She understood beauty.

00:00:46.439 --> 00:00:47.279
She knew

00:00:47.680 --> 00:00:49.119
what kind of cut

00:00:49.959 --> 00:00:51.599
best showed off the body's lines.

00:00:53.439 --> 00:00:54.240
She always said

00:00:56.040 --> 00:00:57.000
only the clothes I made

00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:58.599
were worthy of her soul.

00:01:01.840 --> 00:01:04.160
But her soul was filthy, rotten.

00:01:04.839 --> 00:01:05.559
Darn it

00:01:06.160 --> 00:01:07.800
They all deserved to die.

00:01:11.599 --> 00:01:12.680
Who do you think you are?

00:01:13.639 --> 00:01:14.480
A judge?

00:01:14.720 --> 00:01:15.559
Or a savior?

00:01:17.440 --> 00:01:18.279
A judge?

00:01:19.160 --> 00:01:19.879
A savior?

00:01:21.040 --> 00:01:21.599
No.

00:01:23.319 --> 00:01:24.480
I am just a

00:01:26.639 --> 00:01:27.760
Cleaner.

00:01:29.839 --> 00:01:30.639
Look.

00:01:31.919 --> 00:01:33.199
No matter how expensive the clothes are,

00:01:34.199 --> 00:01:35.279
once they get dirty,

00:01:37.440 --> 00:01:38.599
they can only be destroyed.

00:01:40.599 --> 00:01:42.040
They no longer deserve to exist.

00:01:42.400 --> 00:01:43.160
Do you understand?

00:01:45.599 --> 00:01:46.279
No.

00:01:47.279 --> 00:01:49.120
How could normal people like you understand?

00:01:49.239 --> 00:01:50.199
She...

00:01:51.000 --> 00:01:52.160
Zhou Shuyu,

00:01:53.559 --> 00:01:55.319
had the ability to create life,

00:01:55.800 --> 00:01:57.879
yet threw it away like trash.

00:01:59.440 --> 00:02:00.519
She told me with a smile

00:02:01.879 --> 00:02:03.440
she had aborted the child,

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:06.400
as if she were saying the weather was nice.

00:02:06.959 --> 00:02:08.440
She didn't know how to cherish it.

00:02:09.639 --> 00:02:11.160
She didn't know that was what so many people

00:02:11.919 --> 00:02:12.720
what I...

00:02:14.720 --> 00:02:16.320
what I had dreamed of

00:02:18.399 --> 00:02:20.320
and could never have.

00:02:20.919 --> 00:02:21.679
So?

00:02:22.839 --> 00:02:24.399
You killed her just because of that?

00:02:27.759 --> 00:02:29.320
Just because she had an abortion?

00:02:31.080 --> 00:02:32.000
And because you

00:02:33.639 --> 00:02:35.119
were born with

00:02:37.720 --> 00:02:38.520
Anorchia.

00:02:42.119 --> 00:02:42.960
Just because of that?

00:02:43.199 --> 00:02:44.119
Isn't that enough?

00:02:45.240 --> 00:02:46.679
Isn't that more than enough?

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:50.279
I hated her waste.

00:02:50.679 --> 00:02:51.839
Hated her indifference.

00:02:52.479 --> 00:02:53.759
She desecrated motherhood.

00:02:54.479 --> 00:02:55.320
Desecrated life.

00:02:55.320 --> 00:02:56.759
Then she didn't deserve to have life.

00:02:57.960 --> 00:02:59.000
What about Zhang Chongyang?

00:03:00.199 --> 00:03:01.160
What was his part in this?

00:03:02.839 --> 00:03:03.679
Zhang Chongyang...

00:03:06.119 --> 00:03:08.240
that useless trash who thinks with his crotch.

00:03:09.639 --> 00:03:10.720
If it weren't for him,

00:03:12.240 --> 00:03:13.880
Zhou Shuyu would not have had an abortion.

00:03:14.800 --> 00:03:17.199
They were both trash that needed cleaning up.

00:03:18.279 --> 00:03:18.919
Tell us.

00:03:19.800 --> 00:03:21.479
How did you clean up Zhou Shuyu?

00:03:22.360 --> 00:03:23.800
How did you dispose of her body?

00:03:26.399 --> 00:03:27.360
That tree hollow...

00:03:27.360 --> 00:03:27.960
That day,

00:03:28.240 --> 00:03:30.559
Zhou Shuyu came to me to alter a gown.

00:03:32.240 --> 00:03:33.240
She said,

00:03:34.559 --> 00:03:35.479
"Okay?"

00:03:36.559 --> 00:03:37.440
What is so good about it?

00:03:39.360 --> 00:03:40.800
Teacher Zhou's life isn't good enough?

00:03:41.839 --> 00:03:43.559
A lot of people envy that.

00:03:49.759 --> 00:03:50.639
Teacher Zhou,

00:03:51.160 --> 00:03:52.520
you seem to have lost weight lately.

00:03:55.039 --> 00:03:55.800
Have I?

00:03:59.360 --> 00:04:00.080
Yes.

00:04:02.240 --> 00:04:03.440
A few hours ago,

00:04:05.639 --> 00:04:07.080
there was still a child in here.

00:04:10.759 --> 00:04:11.839
Now it's gone.

00:04:15.160 --> 00:04:16.920
Then take in the waistline a bit more.

00:04:18.119 --> 00:04:20.119
She wanted the most perfect silhouette.

00:04:21.959 --> 00:04:23.920
I told her the most perfect curve

00:04:25.600 --> 00:04:27.359
is the curve of becoming a mother.

00:04:32.519 --> 00:04:33.839
Teacher Zhou doesn't like children.

00:04:38.359 --> 00:04:39.679
She should have liked them.

00:04:43.399 --> 00:04:44.239
But...

00:04:44.959 --> 00:04:47.320
he had to pay for his mistake.

00:04:56.799 --> 00:04:58.640
So I gave her a hand.

00:04:59.720 --> 00:05:00.519
I used an iron

00:05:00.679 --> 00:05:02.640
and smashed her head hard.

00:05:04.519 --> 00:05:05.320
Once.

00:05:07.359 --> 00:05:08.320
Then again.

00:05:09.160 --> 00:05:10.079
Blood.

00:05:12.239 --> 00:05:13.640
Bright red blood.

00:05:15.920 --> 00:05:18.119
Like the finest velvet.

00:05:20.799 --> 00:05:23.040
It was the most beautiful color I had ever seen.

00:05:24.600 --> 00:05:25.920
And that tree hollow

00:05:28.119 --> 00:05:29.760
was the best resting place for her.

00:05:30.760 --> 00:05:32.040
Back to the beginning,

00:05:33.079 --> 00:05:34.760
the place where life is nurtured.

00:05:38.839 --> 00:05:39.760
Quiet.

00:05:42.320 --> 00:05:43.119
Warm.

00:05:45.480 --> 00:05:46.399
Dark.

00:05:49.880 --> 00:05:52.079
Just like the child she killed,

00:05:54.559 --> 00:05:56.119
dead forever.

00:06:07.920 --> 00:06:09.559
Last night you also tried to attack another person.

00:06:13.000 --> 00:06:14.320
She is one of our officers.

00:06:14.679 --> 00:06:15.799
She is still in the hospital.

00:06:16.679 --> 00:06:17.920
Then she deserved it.

00:06:22.959 --> 00:06:23.760
Captain,

00:06:36.040 --> 00:06:37.079
you're not left-handed.

00:07:01.920 --> 00:07:02.679
No, that's not right.

00:07:04.000 --> 00:07:05.040
Something is still off.

00:07:12.959 --> 00:07:14.079
Enough, Zhang Chongyang.

00:07:14.600 --> 00:07:16.000
I know you're pretending to sleep here.

00:07:16.559 --> 00:07:17.799
Ling Han has already confessed everything.

00:07:22.880 --> 00:07:24.040
You look so well-dressed,

00:07:24.040 --> 00:07:25.720
who knew you were so wild in private.

00:07:30.959 --> 00:07:31.839
You don't understand.

00:07:34.119 --> 00:07:35.200
I really loved her.

00:07:36.359 --> 00:07:37.600
So I was willing to indulge

00:07:37.600 --> 00:07:39.119
all of her fetishes.

00:07:40.559 --> 00:07:41.760
To endure the humiliation

00:07:42.040 --> 00:07:43.640
no man could endure.

00:07:47.799 --> 00:07:48.600
But

00:07:50.200 --> 00:07:51.559
I also needed a sense of conquest.

00:07:52.160 --> 00:07:53.399
I also needed release.

00:07:56.160 --> 00:07:57.160
So you went to Chen Ran

00:07:57.160 --> 00:07:58.279
to satisfy that sense of conquest?

00:07:58.600 --> 00:07:59.160
No.

00:08:01.239 --> 00:08:01.760
That's not it.

00:08:04.799 --> 00:08:05.880
Although I cheated,

00:08:08.160 --> 00:08:09.600
I was still in great pain.

00:08:09.920 --> 00:08:11.040
You were in pain?

00:08:11.440 --> 00:08:13.119
When you and Chen Ran were caught in bed,

00:08:14.119 --> 00:08:16.040
who was in pain, Zhou Shuyu or you?

00:08:18.480 --> 00:08:19.720
When she aborted the child,

00:08:20.679 --> 00:08:22.799
you and Chen Ran were healing sweetly in a hotel.

00:08:23.239 --> 00:08:25.040
who was in pain, Zhou Shuyu or you?

00:08:38.760 --> 00:08:40.520
Ling Han's reason for killing was really bizarre

00:08:41.679 --> 00:08:43.760
He treated himself like a moral judge

00:08:44.479 --> 00:08:46.000
Using his twisted values

00:08:46.400 --> 00:08:47.799
to measure other people's lives

00:08:48.840 --> 00:08:49.760
But he forgot

00:08:50.479 --> 00:08:51.640
no matter what the motive is

00:08:52.280 --> 00:08:54.679
no one has the right to take another life

00:08:55.440 --> 00:08:56.080
No one

00:08:56.080 --> 00:08:58.080
can place themselves above the law

00:09:23.320 --> 00:09:24.200
Come on, don't be like this

00:09:24.840 --> 00:09:25.559
Move aside

00:10:03.840 --> 00:10:04.479
Darn it, darn it

00:10:05.599 --> 00:10:06.239
What's wrong?

00:10:09.000 --> 00:10:10.320
I think I'm broken

00:10:12.159 --> 00:10:13.960
My head really hurts

00:10:14.520 --> 00:10:15.119
Well

00:10:15.919 --> 00:10:17.159
The doctor said

00:10:17.359 --> 00:10:18.640
I need rest right now

00:10:19.479 --> 00:10:21.359
When I walk and get jostled around

00:10:21.599 --> 00:10:23.320
my head gets even dizzier

00:10:24.960 --> 00:10:25.760
I'm telling you

00:10:26.280 --> 00:10:27.080
How about

00:10:27.640 --> 00:10:28.280
you carry me

00:10:28.640 --> 00:10:29.760
and carry me to the car

00:10:30.359 --> 00:10:31.599
I'm not asking for much

00:10:31.599 --> 00:10:32.520
Just like this

00:10:32.919 --> 00:10:33.960
A princess carry

00:10:33.960 --> 00:10:34.479
How about it

00:10:34.479 --> 00:10:35.200
How about a Shoulder throw?

00:10:36.119 --> 00:10:36.599
I told you to rest

00:10:36.599 --> 00:10:37.559
If you say one more word

00:10:37.919 --> 00:10:38.960
I'll throw you back in the hospital

00:10:59.559 --> 00:11:00.359
Oh my God

00:11:00.919 --> 00:11:02.880
Why would you even buy something like this?

00:11:03.719 --> 00:11:05.760
Don't you roll your eyes every time

00:11:06.000 --> 00:11:06.919
you see my cartoon pajamas?

00:11:07.679 --> 00:11:08.760
You talk too much

00:11:11.080 --> 00:11:12.479
Last time I saw one by the roadside

00:11:12.760 --> 00:11:13.599
so I just bought it

00:11:18.400 --> 00:11:19.559
Should I turn the AC down a bit?

00:12:14.760 --> 00:12:15.679
This is

00:12:16.599 --> 00:12:18.039
soft anti-collision padding

00:12:18.880 --> 00:12:20.280
When did she put this on?

00:12:38.599 --> 00:12:39.400
Lu Yi

00:12:40.320 --> 00:12:41.520
What should we eat tonight?

00:13:19.239 --> 00:13:20.599
Why does she have the photo?

00:13:21.960 --> 00:13:22.960
This idiot

00:13:23.239 --> 00:13:24.799
Did she have to get involved in this mess?